data.description: Move-in ready! 3 bed/2 bath single story home with two car garage. Walk into the open living room. The Kitchen offers wood cabinetry with breakfast bar. Primary bedroom features built-in shelving and closet, ensuite with tub/shower combo. Nicely sized secondary bedrooms can convert one of the bedrooms into 2! No carpet! Convenient to I-35, local shopping and dining at the Forum.
